 Implement Network Access Control (NAC)
Use Network Access Control to restrict unauthorized devices from accessing the network.

Install FreeRADIUS and configure it with dynamic VLAN assignment.

Install FreeRADIUS:

sudo apt install freeradius
Edit the FreeRADIUS configuration:

sudo nano /etc/freeradius/3.0/mods-enabled/eap
Restart FreeRADIUS:

sudo systemctl restart freeradius
